'''Michael Williams''' (born December 22, 1962), better known by his stage name '''Sister Roma''', is an American [[drag queen]] and [[art director]] of [[gay pornography]]. He is a twenty-year member of San Francisco's [[Sisters of Perpetual Indulgence]].<ref name="Bio">[http://web.archive.org/web/20071012065503/http://thesisters.org/bios/roma.html Personal bio at thesisters.org]</ref>
==Career==
Roma is the [[art director]] at gay pornography studio [[Hot House Entertainment]] and co-hosts an online talk show, ''The Tim and Roma Show,'' that focuses on gay pornographic movies and the [[LGBT]] community. Roma has been a presenter at the [[GayVN Awards]], a pornography industry awards show.<ref>[http://sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/chronicle/archive/2002/06/25/DD127280.DTL Naked Sword And Porn Companies Give Back] San Francisco Bay Time, 5 April 2007 (retrieved 2007-10-29)</ref> Roma has served as an emcee and judge for the San Francisco Drag King Contest,<ref name="Night Crawler: Crown Performance">{{cite web | last =Tudor | first =Silke | title=Night Crawler: Crown Performance | publisher=[[SF Weekly]] | date=July 19, 2000 | url =http://www.sfweekly.com/2000-07-19/news/night-crawler/ | accessdate=2007-07-27}}</ref> the 2005 benefit ''Porn Idol'';<ref name="Will Clark San Francisco">{{cite web | last =Johnson | first =Peter | title=Will Clark San Francisco Fundraisers Near | publisher=[[Adult Video News]] | date=July 19, 2005 | url =http://www.avn.com/index.cfm?objectID=EDA2579E-1372-4B41-C46EDF53A4FA5E3F&slid=174083 | accessdate=2007-11-03}}</ref> and at the [[BDSM]]/leather event the [[Folsom Street Fair]];<ref name="On The Town With Heklina: All">{{cite web | last =Vaziri | first =Aidin | title=On The Town With Heklina: All the city's a stage for this drag queen | publisher=[[San Francisco Chronicle]] | date=October 22, 2006 | url =http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2006/10/22/LVGI9LR7T11.DTL&hw=sister+roma&sn=011&sc=307 | accessdate=2007-10-27}}</ref>
In 2003 Roma's drag act was incorporated into [[Ronnie Larsen]]'s play ''Sleeping With Straight Men'' with [[Mink Stole]] in San Francisco.<ref name="Sleepwalking through a talk-show">{{cite web | last=Hurwitt | first=Robert | title=Sleepwalking through a talk-show tragedy: Jenny Jones drama tends to nod off | publisher=[[San Francisco Chronicle]] | date=September 10, 2003 | url= http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/c/a/2003/09/10/DD47011.DTL&type=printable | accessdate=2007-10-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/default/article/Trash-TV-tragedy-makes-for-farce-Straight-Men-2827060.php|title=Trash-TV tragedy makes for farce: 'Straight Men' a campy success|last=Roca|first=Octavio|date=25 June 2002|work=San Francisco Chronicle|accessdate=2012-07-21}}</ref> In 2006 Roma was nominated for ''Best Nonsexual Performance'' Gay Adult Video News (GAYVN) award for her portrayal of Mona Lott, the maid of ''[[Wet Palms]]'' which is a ten episode gay porn [[soap opera]] series.<ref name="Wet Palms Is A Sexy">{{cite web | last =Van Iquity | first =Sister Dana | title=Wet Palms Is A Sexy Yet Sappy Soap | publisher=[[San Francisco Bay Times]] | date=March 10, 2006 | url =http://www.sfbaytimes.com/article_p.php?article_id=4750 | accessdate= 2007-11-03}}</ref> He also has performed at San Francisco's long-running [[drag (clothing)|drag]] show [[Trannyshack]].<ref name="Tune, out">{{cite web | last=Provenzano | first=Jim | title=Tune, out | publisher=[[Bay Area Reporter]] | date= September 10, 2003 | url=http://www.ebar.com/common/inc/article_print.php?sec=outabout&article=161 | accessdate=2007-10-27}}</ref>
In 2012 Sister Roma was named one of the thirteen grand marshals for the San Francisco Pride Parade.<ref>[http://sfpride.org/parade/grand-marshals.html SF Pride official website]</ref>
